<p xml:id="p.en.2" n="2">Our <rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_526">father</rs> fatal stroke, come, but it is over.</p><space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
<p xml:id="p.en.3" n="3">Van Gogh</p>
